        {
          "id": "2fb61689386a_2",
          "href": null,
          "name": "730a",
          "text": "This morning I am holding space in my mind for what might emerge in my life — after completing the fourth workshop on managing planetary collapse with a beautiful group of awakened people.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
              "end": 145,
              "href": "https://culturalevolutioncenter.org/workshop-on-managing-planetary-collapse/",
              "rel": "",
              "start": 118,
              "title": "",
              "anchorType": "LINK",
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "A",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            }
          ],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "2fb61689386a_3",
          "href": null,
          "name": "7d9f",
          "text": "We held the truth about our planetary predicament with open hearts and open eyes — so that we might begin to apply what we are learning about regenerative economics to restore planetary health over a 50–100 year timespan.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "2fb61689386a_4",
          "href": null,
          "name": "c3c5",
          "text": "I feel called to serve Gaia with the teachings I have learned in the last 25 years so that we might weave a network of existing and newly emergent learning centers around bioregional regeneration.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "2fb61689386a_5",
          "href": null,
          "name": "cc2c",
          "text": "My family is preparing to start a year-long exploration of the world by making ourselves available to travel and stay with communities aligned with this sacred work. We want to help restore human lives and regenerate landscapes so the Earth Healers can do their work.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "2fb61689386a_6",
          "href": null,
          "name": "2169",
          "text": "One key meditation for me has been the difference between being welcomed and being invited — as I have gently imposed myself on welcoming people in the past. This will no longer serve the mission.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
              "end": 72,
              "href": null,
              "rel": null,
              "start": 64,
              "title": null,
              "anchorType": null,
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "EM",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            },
            {
              "end": 90,
              "href": null,
              "rel": null,
              "start": 83,
              "title": null,
              "anchorType": null,
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "EM",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            }
          ],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "2fb61689386a_7",
          "href": null,
          "name": "2577",
          "text": "Now I will only go where I am invited.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "2fb61689386a_8",
          "href": null,
          "name": "4937",
          "text": "How are you participating in the regeneration of Earth? Gaia is calling us to greatness and we have all the tools we need to navigate this planetary predicament and keep humanity part of the Earth for longer than the current centuries-long collapse we are now in.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
              "end": 55,
              "href": null,
              "rel": null,
              "start": 0,
              "title": null,
              "anchorType": null,
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "STRONG",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            }
          ],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "2fb61689386a_9",
          "href": null,
          "name": "1def",
          "text": "I am Gaia knowing Gaia. I see from the satellites she brought forth through my species’ ingenious cultural abilities to see her life systems. And I know her in the ecosystems unraveling from my species’ cultural ability to destroy (or nourish) landscapes.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "2fb61689386a_10",
          "href": null,
          "name": "8606",
          "text": "And so I open myself up to the world and await the next invitation.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "2fb61689386a_11",
          "href": null,
          "name": "d30f",
          "text": "Onward, fellow humans.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "2fb61689386a_12",
          "href": null,
          "name": "4e01",
          "text": "Joe Brewer is the executive director of the Center for Applied Cultural Evolution. Get involved by signing up for our newsletter and consider making a donation to support our work.",
          "metadata": null,
